{"title":"竹","authors":["王鸿"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":11,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王鸿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺拔茁壮的亚龙竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袅娜婆娑的凤尾竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"色彩绚丽的碧玉竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大腹便便的佛肚竹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丛丛簇簇，遍山漫谷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗壮的，用来盖楼造屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚实的，可以制椅打桌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹席、竹箱、竹筒、竹碗、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹勺……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一支支竹童、竹囡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽情倾吐傣家的心曲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各有各的抱负，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各有各的归宿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使被劈成一缕篾丝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要编入箩筐贮存收获。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！西双版纳竹的家族。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}